## 1. 积极性格特征 (Positive Personality Traits)
1. 诚实守信 (honest and trustworthy)
2. 勇敢无畏 (brave and fearless)
3. 乐观向上 (optimistic and positive)
4. 温柔体贴 (gentle and considerate)
5. 坚韧不拔 (tenacious and persistent)
6. 宽宏大量 (magnanimous and generous)
7. 谦虚谨慎 (modest and prudent)
8. 豁达开朗 (open-minded and cheerful)
9. 善解人意 (understanding and sympathetic)
10. 勤劳朴实 (hardworking and plain)
11. 聪明智慧 (clever and wise)
12. 通情达理 (reasonable and sensible)
13. 心胸宽广 (broad-minded)
14. 沉着冷静 (calm and composed)
15. 积极进取 (proactive and enterprising)
16. 自信满满 (full of confidence)
17. 热情洋溢 (enthusiastic and passionate)
18. 坦率直言 (frank and straightforward)
19. 稳重可靠 (steady and reliable)
20. 细心周到 (careful and thoughtful)

## 2. 消极性格特征 (Negative Personality Traits)
21. 虚伪狡诈 (hypocritical and crafty)
22. 冷漠无情 (cold and heartless)
23. 刻薄尖酸 (sharp-tongued and sarcastic)
24. 固执己见 (stubborn and opinionated)
25. 自私自利 (selfish and self-interested)
26. 阴险毒辣 (insidious and vicious)
27. 胆小怕事 (timid and fearful)
28. 贪婪成性 (greedy by nature)
29. 暴躁易怒 (irritable and quick-tempered)
30. 虚荣浮夸 (vain and exaggerated)
31. 懒惰散漫 (lazy and slack)
32. 多疑善变 (suspicious and fickle)
33. 优柔寡断 (irresolute and indecisive)
34. 专横跋扈 (overbearing and domineering)
35. 斤斤计较 (haggle over every penny)
36. 刚愎自用 (headstrong and self-opinionated)
37. 狂妄自大 (arrogant and conceited)
38. 怨天尤人 (blame heaven and others)
39. 心胸狭窄 (narrow-minded)
40. 善妒记恨 (jealous and vindictive)

## 3. 中性性格特征 (Neutral Personality Traits)
41. 内敛沉稳 (reserved and steady)
42. 敏感多思 (sensitive and thoughtful)
43. 理性实际 (rational and practical)
44. 随性洒脱 (casual and unrestrained)
45. 追求完美 (perfectionist)
46. 慎重考虑 (cautious and thoughtful)
47. 果断利落 (decisive and efficient)
48. 感性直觉 (sensitive and intuitive)
49. 独立自主 (independent and autonomous)
50. 深沉内敛 (profound and reserved)
51. 有条不紊 (methodical and orderly)
52. 率真自然 (genuine and natural)
53. 冷静客观 (calm and objective)
54. 细腻敏锐 (delicate and keen)
55. 从善如流 (readily accept good advice)
56. 喜静不喜动 (prefer quietness over activity)
57. 喜动不喜静 (prefer activity over quietness)
58. 一板一眼 (rigid and inflexible)
59. 顺其自然 (let things take their course)
60. 善变灵活 (changeable and flexible)

## 4. 社交性格特征 (Social Personality Traits)
61. 外向活泼 (outgoing and lively)
62. 内向害羞 (introverted and shy)
63. 八面玲珑 (smooth in dealing with people)
64. 长袖善舞 (adept in social activities)
65. 圆滑世故 (sophisticated and worldly-wise)
66. 孤僻冷漠 (solitary and aloof)
67. 热情好客 (warm and hospitable)
68. 慷慨大方 (generous)
69. 吝啬小气 (stingy and mean)
70. 平易近人 (affable and approachable)
71. 高傲自负 (proud and conceited)
72. 谦恭有礼 (modest and polite)
73. 油嘴滑舌 (glib and slick)
74. 嘴甜心苦 (sweet in words but bitter at heart)
75. 心直口快 (straightforward)
76. 心口不一 (say one thing and mean another)
77. 待人友善 (friendly to others)
78. 深居简出 (live in seclusion)
79. 不拘小节 (not fussy about trifles)
80. 细致入微 (meticulous and thorough)

## 5. 工作性格特征 (Work-related Personality Traits)
81. 雷厉风行 (resolute and decisive)
82. 井井有条 (neat and orderly)
83. 一丝不苟 (meticulous)
84. 马马虎虎 (careless and casual)
85. 精益求精 (strive for perfection)
86. 敬业专注 (dedicated and focused)
87. 拖拉散漫 (procrastinating and slack)
88. 分秒必争 (fight for every minute and second)
89. 废寝忘食 (forget to sleep and eat)
90. 兢兢业业 (cautious and conscientious)
91. 得过且过 (muddle along)
92. 严于律己 (strict with oneself)
93. 独当一面 (able to take charge)
94. 循规蹈矩 (conform to rules)
95. 墨守成规 (adhere to old ways)
96. 标新立异 (create new ways)
97. 埋头苦干 (work hard silently)
98. 锲而不舍 (persistent)
99. 处变不惊 (remain calm in face of changes)
100. 随机应变 (adapt to changing conditions)

## 6. 情绪性格特征 (Emotional Personality Traits)
101. 情绪稳定 (emotionally stable)
102. 喜怒无常 (moody)
103. 心平气和 (peaceful and calm)
104. 焦躁不安 (restless and fidgety)
105. 悲观消沉 (pessimistic and depressed)
106. 满怀希望 (full of hope)
107. 多愁善感 (sentimental and melancholy)
108. 波澜不惊 (unperturbed)
109. 情感丰富 (emotionally rich)
110. 冷若冰霜 (cold as ice)
111. 心如止水 (heart like still water)
112. 感情外露 (wear heart on sleeve)
113. 心事重重 (full of worries)
114. 忧心忡忡 (deeply worried)
115. 漠不关心 (indifferent)
116. 心急如焚 (anxious)
117. 心如刀割 (heart-broken)
118. 心慌意乱 (flustered and confused)
119. 心旷神怡 (carefree and happy)
120. 愁眉苦脸 (worried look)

## 7. 思维方式特征 (Thinking Style Traits)
121. 思维敏捷 (quick-minded)
122. 头脑灵活 (agile mind)
123. 反应迟钝 (slow response)
124. 思路清晰 (clear thinking)
125. 目光长远 (farsighted)
126. 目光短浅 (shortsighted)
127. 深思熟虑 (think deeply and thoroughly)
128. 异想天开 (fantasize)
129. 脚踏实地 (practical and down-to-earth)
130. 天马行空 (unfettered imagination)
131. 心胸开阔 (broad-minded)
132. 心胸狭隘 (narrow-minded)
133. 思维缜密 (rigorous thinking)
134. 发散思维 (divergent thinking)
135. 触类旁通 (learn by analogy)
136. 举一反三 (infer other cases from one instance)
137. 融会贯通 (integrate knowledge)
138. 思如泉涌 (thoughts gushing like a spring)
139. 脑洞大开 (full of wild ideas)
140. 条理分明 (logical and orderly)

## 8. 行为模式特征 (Behavioral Pattern Traits)
141. 谨小慎微 (cautious and careful)
142. 莽撞冲动 (rash and impulsive)
143. 雷厉风行 (efficient and decisive)
144. 优柔寡断 (indecisive)
145. 举止优雅 (elegant manners)
146. 粗鲁无礼 (rude and impolite)
147. 彬彬有礼 (polite and courteous)
148. 蛮不讲理 (unreasonable)
149. 礼尚往来 (reciprocate courtesy)
150. 有恩必报 (repay kindness)
151. 目中无人 (arrogant and disrespectful)
152. 一诺千金 (a promise worth a thousand gold)
153. 出尔反尔 (go back on one's word)
154. 克己奉公 (selfless devotion)
155. 见风使舵 (change according to circumstances)
156. 风雨无阻 (rain or shine)
157. 见利忘义 (forget righteousness at the sight of profit)
158. 重信守诺 (keep one's word)
159. 自律严格 (strictly self-disciplined)
160. 我行我素 (do as one pleases)

## 9. 复合性格特征 (Complex Personality Traits)
161. 刚正不阿 (upright and incorruptible)
162. 义薄云天 (highly righteous)
163. 光明磊落 (frank and aboveboard)
164. 阴险狡诈 (treacherous and cunning)
165. 自命不凡 (consider oneself extraordinary)
166. 谦谦君子 (modest gentleman)
167. 锋芒毕露 (showing off one's brilliance)
168. 深藏不露 (keeping one's talents hidden)
169. 明哲保身 (sensible and self-protective)
170. 舍己为人 (self-sacrificing)
171. 临危不惧 (fearless in danger)
172. 忠肝义胆 (loyal and righteous)
173. 温文尔雅 (gentle and elegant)
174. 粗犷豪放 (rough and bold)
175. 战战兢兢 (trembling with fear)
176. 大义凛然 (strongly righteous)
177. 桀骜不驯 (untamed and rebellious)
178. 心怀鬼胎 (harbor evil intentions)
179. 仗义执言 (speak out for justice)
180. 沉默寡言 (silent and few words)

## 10. 性格对比词汇 (Personality Contrast Vocabulary)
181. 慷慨大方 vs. 吝啬小气 (generous vs. stingy)
182. 勇敢无畏 vs. 胆小怕事 (brave vs. timid)
183. 诚实守信 vs. 弄虚作假 (honest vs. dishonest)
184. 活泼开朗 vs. 沉默寡言 (lively vs. taciturn)
185. 冲动鲁莽 vs. 深思熟虑 (impulsive vs. thoughtful)
186. 坚韧不拔 vs. 半途而废 (persistent vs. quitting halfway)
187. 积极乐观 vs. 消极悲观 (optimistic vs. pessimistic)
188. 温柔体贴 vs. 粗暴蛮横 (gentle vs. rough)
189. 随和友善 vs. 固执己见 (easygoing vs. stubborn)
190. 谦虚谨慎 vs. 狂妄自大 (modest vs. arrogant)
191. 恭敬有礼 vs. 目中无人 (respectful vs. disrespectful)
192. 雷厉风行 vs. 拖泥带水 (efficient vs. procrastinating)
193. 心胸宽广 vs. 斤斤计较 (broad-minded vs. petty)
194. 仗义执言 vs. 明哲保身 (outspoken vs. self-protective)
195. 沉着冷静 vs. 暴躁易怒 (calm vs. irritable)
196. 独立自主 vs. 依赖他人 (independent vs. dependent)
197. 大胆创新 vs. 墨守成规 (innovative vs. conventional)
198. 轻松幽默 vs. 严肃刻板 (humorous vs. serious)
199. 热情洋溢 vs. 冷漠疏离 (passionate vs. aloof)
200. 简单直接 vs. 复杂多变 (simple vs. complex)

